\c 85 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 85\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Jireenyi Akka Iddootti Deebifamuuf Kadhachuu(Geggeessituu warra faarfatootaaf; faarfannaa ilmaan Qoraahi)
\m \bd 1\bd* Takka biyya keetti faara tolteetta, yaa Waaqayyo! Yaaqoobiif adda kenniteetta;
\m \bd 2\bd* saba keef yakka isaa dhiifteettaaf, cubbuun isaanii hundinuus deebi'ee akka hin mul'anne gooteetta.
\m \bd 3\bd* Finiina dheekkamsa kee hundumaa irraa deebifteetta, aarii kee isa boba'us dhiifteetta.
\m \bd 4\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo isa fayyina nuuf laattuu, iddootti nu deebisi; nutti gadduun kee haa hafu.
\m \bd 5\bd* Ati bara baraan nutti dheekkamtaa ree? Aaruu kees dhalootaa hamma dhalootaatti itti fuftaa ree?
\m \bd 6\bd* Sabni kee akka sitti gammadutti, deebitee lubbuu nutti hin deebiftuu ree?
\m \bd 7\bd* Gaarummaa kee nu argisiisi, yaa Waaqayyo, gargaarsa kee isa fayyisu nuuf kenni!
\m \bd 8\bd* Wanta Waaqayyo dubbatu dhaggeeffachuu nan barbaada; sabni isaa warri isaaf of kennan, gara gowwummaatti hin deebi'in malee, gooftichi nagaa isaanitti in dubbata.
\m \bd 9\bd* Dhuguma iyyuu fayyisuun isaa warra isa sodaataniif dhi'oo dha; kanaaf ulfinni biyya keenya keessa in buufata.
\m \bd 10\bd* Gaarummaanii fi amanamummaan wal in argu, qajeelummaa fi nagaan wal in dhungatu.
\m \bd 11\bd* Amanamummaan lafa keessaa in biqila, qajeelummaan waaqa keessaa gad in ilaala.
\m \bd 12\bd* dhugumaan Waaqayyo waan gaarii in kenna, lafti keenyas midhaan in baasa;
\m \bd 13\bd* qajeelummaan fuula gooftichaa dura in adeema, faanni isaas isa duukaa in qajeela.
